{"tid":1359803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］個人建議 唔好再話我係分化撚 我講事實咋","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:57:34.000Z","uid":169960,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7204301c3cf5f3ad3fc7089a61870d7fe10c29d0","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"唔該你地個個睇嘢睇晒成篇 <br />\n成日睇啲唔睇啲又話人分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下一切都係尋晚周公話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">首先</span>我想講嘅係女仔盡量唔好企咁前 想企前嘅可以 但大家一齊練好體能先<br />\n自問自己一直做開運動 但面對住現場對抗個下完全係手無縛雞之力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前企好前 身邊男仔都唔準 但自己情緒控制唔好 一見到班警犬打自己手足 就嬲到跑到最前 <br />\n<br />\n但直到沙田個日同班警犬正面對抗先察覺到 女仔就算用盡力 你都冇乜用 <br />\n<br />\n個日係新城市廣場d人推嚟推去 而你已經係俾人夾住 連推都冇得推 俾自己手足撞到企唔穩 好彩捉得夠實 如果唔係一個跌就會衍生人踩人 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女仔們 我知你好想幫手 我都好想幫手 <br />\n但我哋企到咁前但又唔夠力 <br />\n搞到身邊啲男仔好擔心又要take care我哋<br />\n佢哋會分心 <br />\n<br />\n試學嗰啲格鬥技巧唔係冇用<br />\n但我哋連力都冇 <br />\n到時用都未用到已經俾人捉實咗<br />\n所以唔好諗住一步登天<br />\n 由今日體能 重力訓練 開始 慢慢嚟 我地係長期抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我絕對唔係分咩男女 係個人經歷真心建議 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二</span>請自己準備好物資 唔好再依靠物資站<br />\n自己嘅防裝自己準備好 <br />\n有時真係唔小心帶少咗個眼罩 <br />\n但去到物資站已經唔夠派<br />\n請唔好老奉去物資拎gear 大家都有責任保護好自己<br />\n如果一次半次唔記得帶冇所謂<br />\n但唔好唔好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好依賴 記得full gear上陣 你唔驚 但你隔離嘅人會擔心你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第三</span>拎大聲公咁傳遞資訊嘅人可唔可以表達多少少<br />\n依家大家同前線都唔會割席<br />\n好似嗰日喺上環有拎大聲公人講1125一齊走<br />\n之後大家嘅反應都係去同前線講唔好同我地講<br />\n但其實1125個時間本身好似已經同前線傾好咗<br />\n<br />\n所以如果可以講多一句講多少少 <br />\n例如：已經同前線傾好咗 1125我地大家一齊走<br />\n個人流疏通會好好多<br />\n因為有好多人都擔心前線唔會走<br />\n但自己走咗唔敢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後</span>唔好再話我係鬼係分化撚 因為好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同埋希望元朗嗰日會見到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦大家了</span>"},{"pid":"515335ea6025f19e6084f6a4a6588278d9014e9d","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dceff12200ec968680e40344913c7fe44dd9042","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋如果身邊嘅人有連登ac 幫手叫佢地推翻啲有用嘅post上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a7d36333aca49bc722615b6e9cab78628ac6f034","tid":1359803,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6afb43dcb9b52cef944be2ec1d1ca40b263b7996","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b0beb038ee7c75bf39df43baa96a97ae6e599b10","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed4a6d8136e8dd8a08f48be99354d9a315b259f9","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e402a1e2e4715556c64f11e34ec512c12692b78","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2de585d4f51b4405ef1be14e93db54e5ac261518","tid":1359803,"uid":272663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"推！辛苦了"},{"pid":"05132f8e71ee87d51f89305a56c6c02ead958ccf","tid":1359803,"uid":179963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n良好溝通好重要<br />\n<br />\nkeypoint講多一句就好唔同"},{"pid":"52bdd20f8dfca842f1ecdceb368631dac80810a9","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"299ad04d2206eeb6b478ee4b71c87cb0e9758d5c","tid":1359803,"uid":37924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>兄弟爬山 各有各做 不割蓆<br />\n支持支援前線 中排 後援<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1baf33b5b4d869dcb56917b2895c090574058a90","tid":1359803,"uid":169960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc92d3280e0a19096acd5f42d8cfe923